title: Kat Moss from Scowl
itunes:title: Kat Moss from Scowl
description:
I have a treat for you, Kat Moss from Scowl comes to hang out with us today! The band has turned a lot of heads within the hardcore and punk world, so I had to have her on the show. We discuss a lot of things including her being a "horse girl", fashion and RBS (real bay shit). It's an insightful conversation and stoked to have had it. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
